- **Super-domain-level RBAC is coarse.** Everyone authorized for `Healthcare` sees every basin in Healthcare. Some real-world regimes need finer cuts (e.g., a clinical researcher should see SNOMED diagnoses but not RxNorm prescriptions for the same patient).
